{"tid":2468444,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"原神打手超級毒能  正式復活 連仔請處理","createTime":"2021-03-30T13:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T16:31:53.000Z","uid":45498,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"574b53a6c0424b832a24a7ccba8e9c9c774a3e1a","tid":2468444,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWJgs52qu25q1nuBL3B5jJX79tamKUGKCdfwFPYdZ65t2?filename=vOPLyMv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOPLyMv.png&h=0fe4039a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超級毒能已回歸 <br />\n成為P牌仔<br />\n連燈巴打 #379900 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個新user無固狙擊滋擾我 <br />\n原來係因為我高調反原神 <br />\n因為舊AC被封鎖作出報復行為<br />\n<br />\n《原神》擺明照抄Zelda , 照樣上Switch<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824509</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共通點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 原神頭號打手 開post為原神護航宣傳<br />\n<br />\n遊戲台有冇人夠超級毒能on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073626/page/4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073626/page/4</a><br />\n<br />\n此post提及其身分為知名原神打手<br />\n<br />\n連燈巴打重覆相同行為 <br />\n包括冷清嘅原神Post <br />\n<br />\n以及附和其他打手<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfJci9feCBPiEEFbp77m1zTawsSZ63aiP5Y94U3eBC9gR?filename=t7KWFyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7KWFyr.png&h=904f2432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWtTakn648t6eM2CpuZS8qquHfJgZxt9PYHkq1RzLr3ve?filename=vjTDTTs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvjTDTTs.png&h=ea505368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每當他人提起其打手身份<br />\n即發難屈人宣傳原神<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNrpyCsS7CKaZrws7QrUVAm6U8oPgSJMy2gkYGzycpQww?filename=SF4jDHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSF4jDHB.png&h=52d61c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 對其他用戶進行滋擾<br />\n<br />\n超級毒能時期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連燈打手時期<br />\n<br />\n針對本人開Post<br />\n<br />\n甚至開網典頁面進行滋擾 <br />\n因我引用慕容公子影片去指證<br />\nCGA、電競總會、政府之間的關係、<br />\n屎家軍等KOL利益集團<br />\n理據充分無法反駁，引起其不斷人身攻擊<br />\n形容本人為慕容腦殘粉 <br />\n<br />\n網典admin已刪除<br />\n有關無意義人身攻擊嘅內容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人對其他主題嘅回覆亦受到影響<br />\n佢全力護航原神 批鬥黃營KOL <br />\n<br />\n無人理會仍然開post/狙擊式回覆無限批鬥<br />\n例如本人反對批鬥大J  <br />\n連燈巴打即無限上綱上線<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQWt8fu5DvwHEz3TcxhdTJtYDy4qpATr5Yuz3ovw4n1N2?filename=6N2dHPQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6N2dHPQ.png&h=42f09684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大J出片屌屌柒鐘生了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2463931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2463931</a><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">此post樓主其實係我其他Post嘅成員</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme7m57esHgY5cywKhKDA5VJuYwgQRr1SM8AqHLvpZ2DAs?filename=DpArioP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpArioP.png&h=3c443a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重覆針對大J曾玩LOL一事不斷批鬥<br />\n本人數度解釋因為LOL社群有大量支持香港嘅玩家<br />\n所以不願分化 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXb5fHDGBmmtP1wFjo4EWB9ugKLXqxdLz78ECBj9PGM7V?filename=VOXtwVi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOXtwVi.png&h=c3e2687d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而佢一再借同一點攻擊我/LOL玩家/個別Youtuber及其支持者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其打手目的及五毛立場明顯<br />\n已受舉報但其行為未見改善<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmakhaWtKgw9L7ympow2vXUXYefat9r3QmFQVzJ1ePGpeS?filename=Q2WYT9M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2WYT9M.png&h=3ee719ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩人嘅滋擾手段、護航原神嘅行徑完全一致<br />\n請連仔處理各位原神打手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論其身份是否超級毒能本人<br />\n行為舉止同樣引起相同問題<br />\n請admin 盡早處理"},{"pid":"dcdc0e0dd4fe1732fdfca0880bf4d7e8ddc99a69","tid":2468444,"uid":379900,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6865d638adb3e8893b699d3e3c653b53c5c0ee5b","tid":2468444,"uid":45498,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"引用公告<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">網路打手、分身帳號</span><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG 是一個自由的討論平台，我們歡迎所有會員自由表達意見。<br />\n管理團隊對所有會員一視同仁，不會因政見及立場不同無故封鎖會員帳號，但我們絕不容許有人利用本討論區，有組織性或惡意煽動他人、操控輿論或達到個別目的。<br />\n因此<span class=\"gold\">我們一直都有封鎖各種類型、包括俗稱「五毛」的集團式網絡打手帳號</span>。<br />\n<br />\n我們在此強調，<span class=\"red\">本討論區禁止使用分身帳號及所有網絡打手行為</span>，管理團隊將會持續監察有關行為，一經發現將會封鎖帳號。<br />\n如用戶發現疑似網絡打手或其他任何違反使用條款情況，請使用「舉報功能」向我們反映，我們將會深入調查及處理。"},{"pid":"a733fa0805bcee89e874c34486de0c0cc26cdf90","tid":2468444,"uid":241804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"嘩屌呀，原來佢係超級毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451642fbbad8f7fa9ad63fcc023371fd41102b2a","tid":2468444,"uid":45498,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a733fa0805bcee89e874c34486de0c0cc26cdf90","tid":2468444,"uid":241804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"嘩屌呀，原來佢係超級毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-30T13:31:55.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對我仇口又俾我搞到咁大<br />\n係得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/d